IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Brook Ann EGGELING and Adam Conrad Eggeling Upon the Petition of Brook Ann Eggeling, n/k/a Brook Ann Lapke, Petitioner-Appellant/Cross-Appellee, And Concerning Adam Conrad Eggeling, Respondent-Appellee/Cross-Appellant. No. 18-0234 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A former wife appeals a modification order granting physical care of their two children to her former husband; the former husband cross appeals. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
